{"tid":1805913,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【迎2020】金拱門1月2日起加價 板燒雞腿餐由脆辣雞腿餐取代改售$27","createTime":"2020-01-01T02:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T07:41:19.000Z","uid":51620,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"25bb1eafb308fb18296ebab0cb414d7f09c6d153","tid":1805913,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:45:07.000Z","msg":"麥當勞宣佈明日（2日）清晨4時起部份食品加價，平均加幅約2%，當中歷年來劃一價錢和劃一加幅的超值套餐，新一年起分為3個價錢，其中6件麥樂雞餐維持$25；雙層芝士漢堡餐加價$1至$26，加幅4%；板燒雞腿包餐由脆辣雞腿包餐取代，定價$27。<br />\n<br />\n部份食品加價$0.5或$1。升級至加大套餐或大大啖組合、單點細薯條加價$0.5，醒神超值選（$14麥芝蛋飽醒晨超值選除外）、超值早晨套餐、超值套餐、The Signature Collection套餐、開心樂園餐、A+B下午茶餐、3款超值選（芝蛋脆雞飽、豬柳蛋漢堡、2件脆香雞翼）加價$1。<br />\n<br />\n價格維持不變除$25麥樂雞餐和$14麥芝蛋包早餐外，還有$13麥旋風、$6細汽水、第4年無加價的$11魚柳飽、$$8新地和$7蘋果批。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞解釋，面對營運成本上升，及社會事件輕微影響生意，部份產品需微調價格，加幅較綜合食品指數的約3%溫和。麥當勞元旦日起一連8天推出每天限定優惠，較去年連續14天優惠少，其中今日凌晨4時至晚上11時59分推出全日供應精選早晨套餐及珍寶套餐，售$27及$30，兩款都較去年元旦日加價$1。其他優惠包括$10九件麥樂雞等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200101/60437235?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60437235%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0asxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=da72a73c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60437235%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=43abc67c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200101/60437235?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a>"},{"pid":"3942780f3a3f03a59a0a1b570dd35d7f6b5b2522","tid":1805